Package gov.sandia.geotess.extensions.rstt

Class Uncertainty

java.lang.Object
gov.sandia.geotess.extensions.rstt.Uncertainty
Direct Known Subclasses:
UncertaintyPDU, UncertaintyPIU
public abstract class Uncertainty
extends java.lang.Object
Base class for UncertaintySLBM and UncertaintyPathDep. Contains the enums to convert phase and attribute strings from numbers-to-strings and strings-to- numbers. Also stores the fields fileName and phaseNum which are common to both derived classes.
Author:
jrhipp
